## 🌍 5. Deploy It Online

Show a **live version** of your site — recruiters love seeing that it works.

- **Frontend:** Deploy to **Vercel** or **Netlify**
- **Backend:** Deploy to **Render**, **Railway**, or **Cyclic**
- **Database:** Use **MongoDB Atlas**

Ensure CORS is correctly configured (`cors()` middleware in Express).

---

## 🧠 6. Bonus Polish Ideas

- Add a **loading spinner** for data fetches.
- Use **React Router v6** for smooth navigation.
- Implement **form validation** using `react-hook-form`.
- Use meaningful color palette — professional neutrals (white/gray/blue).
- Add a **favicon and meta tags**.

---

## 🧾 7. Optional: Improve Certificate Verification System

If you also include your **certificate verification project**, base it on [litch07/eduauth-registry](https://github.com/litch07/eduauth-registry) — MERN + secure JWT + email verification. You can host both projects as part of your portfolio (“Web Development Suite”).

